1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 18=

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,790
Your Majesty has been
worried about Shandong lately?

22
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,310
The disaster was quelled long ago.

23
00:01:33,350 --> 00:01:34,760
But someone embezzled relief grain.

24
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,040
It stirred public anger.

25
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,320
Now,

26
00:01:37,510 --> 00:01:39,000
unrest has broken out in several places.

27
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,790
Really?

28
00:01:41,590 --> 00:01:44,870
I heard the leader
is Consort Duan's father.

29
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:46,510
He has always been cautious.

30
00:01:46,790 --> 00:01:48,040
How could he make such a mistake?

31
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,480
There is no conclusion yet.

32
00:01:49,790 --> 00:01:51,000
I will not judge rashly.

33
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,480
Your Majesty, have some soup.

34
00:02:13,470 --> 00:02:14,360
Your Majesty.

35
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:16,630
Your Majesty, you seem to...

36
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:18,430
have developed pox.

37
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,520
This...

38
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,240
This...

39
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,280
Bring me a mirror now!

40
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:44,470
I just applied the medicine.

41
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,430
Endure a little longer.

42
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,560
The itching will stop soon.

43
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,800
Why don't you wear a veil?

44
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:51,240
If you get infected by me...

45
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,590
If I can share your suffering,
Your Majesty,

46
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,870
it is my blessing.

47
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:04,000
The medicine is ready.

48
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,710
Please take it, Your Majesty.

49
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,360
Let me do it.

50
00:03:23,590 --> 00:03:24,710
I added extra licorice root,

51
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:25,750
so it isn't bitter at all.

52
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,630
This illness of mine

53
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,030
showed me people's true colors.

54
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,640
Noble Lady Hui,

55
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:50,520
you are so thoughtful.

56
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,400
I'm just being bold.

57
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:56,030
The other ladies
are also loyal to Your Majesty.

58
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,750
They just dare not disturb your rest.

59
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,190
You are such a kind and sincere person.

60
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:04,280
I only hope you can recover peacefully.

61
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,840
But,

62
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:11,240
I think this pox outbreak is suspicious.

63
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,640
Oh?

64
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,430
Why do you say that?

65
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:17,360
Consort Duan never left her palace
for her pregnancy.

66
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,430
Yet she was the first to get infected.

67
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,800
It is too much of a coincidence.

68
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:25,920
Consort Duan says her smallpox

69
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,600
was a setup by Consort Lan.

70
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:30,310
So she has been
cursing Consort Lan nonstop.

71
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,110
Sixi.

72
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,120
Yes.

73
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,480
Investigate this thoroughly.

74
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,560
Yes.

75
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:53,000
Why?

76
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,800
Why does His Majesty suddenly
want to investigate the pox source?

77
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,270
News from the Qianqing Palace says

78
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,120
His Majesty has contracted pox.

79
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:02,310
And suffers terribly every day.

80
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,870
It is inevitable for him to overthink.

81
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:07,270
He finds the pox outbreak
in the harem full of doubts.

82
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,600
We covered our tracks perfectly,

83
00:05:10,850 --> 00:05:12,120
but digging deep

84
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,600
might uncover flaws.

85
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:24,680
Only the dead keep secrets forever.

86
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,520
You go there.

87
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,870
Make the one who should disappear
vanish forever.

88
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,390
But Consort Duan once named us directly

89
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,720
in her accusation.

90
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,070
Back then,
the Empress Dowager and His Majesty

91
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:40,680
only thought
she was falsely accusing you

92
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,870
out of hatred for you.

93
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,430
If someone dies now,

94
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,390
won't we become more suspicious?

95
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,720
I can't care about that anymore.

96
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,920
If the evidence falls into their hands,

97
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,920
I'll be done for completely.

98
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:53,070
If they have no evidence,

99
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,040
even if they suspect me,

100
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,190
they can do nothing to me.

101
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,800
Hurry and get this done.

102
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,920
(Counting the time.)

103
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:16,870
(Zuo Zhuan)
(Consort Lan should make a move now.)

104
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,680
Your Highness,
may I ask you a favor?

105
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:35,910
Sit down.

106
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:43,710
Come closer.

107
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,150
Alright.

108
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,430
I haven't even told you what it is.

109
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,430
And you agreed so readily.

110
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,560
Then,

111
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:10,310
what if I ask you to kill someone?

112
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:15,630
This is my token.

113
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,360
My men

114
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,720
are yours to command.

115
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,320
(Command)
No need.

116
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:25,270
I just want you to help me save someone.

117
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:26,840
Alright.

118
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:29,920
Thank you, Your Highness.

119
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:50,270
My Lords, have you worked out a plan?

120
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:53,720
How should we treat
His Majesty's illness?

121
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,720
Noble Lady Hui,

122
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,270
over these past few days,

123
00:07:57,270 --> 00:08:00,040
we have carefully observed
His Majesty's condition.

124
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:02,070
We find it very suspicious.

125
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:03,920
Combined with the cases of Consort Duan

126
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,630
and the 14th Prince,

127
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:09,000
we think His Majesty
does not have smallpox.

128
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,310
If it is not smallpox, then what is it?

129
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:14,270
It is a similar illness.

130
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:17,000
People call it chickenpox.

131
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,870
It usually heals on its own.

132
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,240
When the fever subsides,

133
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,000
His Majesty will recover naturally.

134
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,680
We have prescribed fever-reducing
medicine for His Majesty.

135
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:28,390
It will be ready to take once decocted.

136
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,320
Chickenpox.

137
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,720
(She truly foresees everything.)

138
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,910
(Everything is within her expectation.)

139
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,080
The one you asked me to save.

140
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,270
I've already saved.

141
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,320
Thank you, Your Highness.

142
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,320
When my men arrived,

143
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,200
he was on the verge of death.

144
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,390
You truly

145
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:00,790
foresee everything.

146
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,440
Just a coincidence.

147
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,960
Just a coincidence.

148
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,480
Come dine with me.

149
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,750
Alright.

150
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:16,030
How is the dinner tonight?

151
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,230
Very sumptuous.

152
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,600
Is there anything different from usual?

153
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,600
Is there anything different?

154
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:25,120
Today's sweet bun, steamed rice cake

155
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,000
and this shrimp with egg white

156
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,630
are not palace dishes.

157
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:30,910
From an outside restaurant?

158
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,840
No.

159
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,200
These three delicacies

160
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,480
are Fulong Town specialties.

161
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,670
My men just brought them back.

162
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,270
Fulong Town?

163
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,320
Your men are so thoughtful.

164
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,120
They bring you souvenirs
when on business.

165
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,240
You don't know where Fulong Town is?

166
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,040
No, I don't.

167
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,440
Then do you know Shen Dazhu?

168
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,870
No, I don't.

169
00:09:53,930 --> 00:09:54,770
What's wrong?

170
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:55,870
Why do you ask?

171
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,550
Nothing.

172
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,910
Forget it, if you don't.

173
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:00,200
I just asked casually.

174
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,200
Please, Your Highness.

175
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,840
Your Highness, how's it going?

176
00:10:06,270 --> 00:10:07,390
Just as expected.

177
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:09,320
She is not Ye Jin at all.

178
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,800
Your Highness.

179
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,000
You have tested her?

180
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,120
Fulong Town is Ye Jin's hometown.

181
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:16,910
Shen Dazhu is Ye Jin's father.

182
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:18,910
But when I mentioned

183
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:21,120
Fulong Town and Shen Dazhu to her,

184
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:22,840
she showed no reaction at all.

185
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,380
Oh no.

186
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,320
My cover is blown.

187
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,720
How can I explain this?

188
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,710
Who's there?

189
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:32,240
It's me. It's me.

190
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,080
Let go.

191
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,040
It hurts.

192
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,750
You may leave. I will handle this.

193
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,080
Yes.

194
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:51,470
Easy, easy.

195
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,360
Actually,

196
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,840
I was an orphan.

197
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:14,510
My uncle seized all I had
and sold me into a brothel.

198
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,720
I ran away desperately at that time.

199
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,200
But I had no money,

200
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,480
and I almost starved to death.

201
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:22,670
Luckily,
I met the palace maid selection team.

202
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,320
That eunuch saved me.

203
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:27,510
The real Ye Jin died of illness.

204
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,670
He was afraid of being blamed,

205
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:30,120
so he made me take Ye Jin's identity.

206
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:32,510
Your Highness,

207
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:36,000
I entered the palace just to survive.

208
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,630
I could never assassinate His Majesty.

209
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:40,510
And I mean no harm

210
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:41,870
to the Empress Dowager and you.

211
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,870
Your Highness, please show me mercy

212
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,120
and spare my life.

213
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,600
Actually, whether you are Ye Jin or not.

214
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,000
I don't care.

215
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,200
Then...

216
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,830
Then...

217
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,030
Your Highness, you're...

218
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:58,790
I just wanted to prove my guess.

219
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:00,790
What guess?

220
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:02,870
Do you remember

221
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:06,480
the story of the Imperial Preceptor?

222
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:07,960
Yes.

223
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,440
Then do you know his fate?

224
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:11,240
I don't.

225
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:13,320
(This isn't in the novel.)

226
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:15,120
After my father ascended the throne,

227
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,960
he was impeached by all the ministers.

228
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:18,440
He took all the blame

229
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,200
for father's rise to the throne.

230
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,840
In the end,

231
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,790
he was executed as a sorcerer.

232
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,280
Oh my god.

233
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:32,600
I have destroyed all your files.

234
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,600
Ye Jin's parents

235
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,150
have also been settled properly.

236
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:37,910
From today on,

237
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:39,750
you are Ye Jin.

238
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,440
Do you remember that?

239
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:44,200
I do. I remember.

240
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,510
I'll do it myself.

241
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:49,480
Thank you, Your Highness.

242
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,840
Your Majesty.

243
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:53,790
Your Majesty.

244
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:01,720
What time is it?

245
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:03,510
Why is it dark?

246
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:04,720
It's already the You hour.

247
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,240
The Imperial Physician said
your fever just broke.

248
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,320
You can't sleep any longer.

249
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:10,440
You need to wake up
and circulate your qi.

250
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,510
Why are you here?

251
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:20,600
Weren't you told to trace

252
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,840
the source of the pox?

253
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:22,960
Your Majesty,

254
00:13:23,190 --> 00:13:24,030
I

255
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,270
have found out everything.

256
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,120
Take your medicine first, Your Majesty.

257
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,630
You've been unconscious with
a high fever these days.

258
00:13:36,910 --> 00:13:38,030
Health is the most important.

259
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,790
Take the medicine first.

260
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:40,960
Then you can hear the report.

261
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,000
Sixi, you speak first.

262
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,120
I'm listening.

263
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:46,080
But, Your Majesty, this...

264
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,630
Noble Lady Hui
doesn't need to step aside.

265
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:51,960
Just speak.

266
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:52,870
Yes.

267
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:55,320
I followed the clues

268
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:58,240
and finally found Chief Eunuch Li
of the Imperial Household.

269
00:13:58,620 --> 00:14:00,320
But Chief Eunuch Li
was not in the palace.

270
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:02,510
So I sent men to look for him.

271
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:05,200
They found his private residence today.

272
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:07,630
It is not a place
for an ordinary servant,

273
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:10,840
but a mansion for second-rank officials.

274
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,550
I was about to arrest him
and bring him back.

275
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,840
But someone tried to
assassinate him on the way.

276
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,200
He was terrified.

277
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,630
When he heard Your Majesty summoned him,

278
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:22,000
he confessed immediately
without torture.

279
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:24,630
Consort Duan's case was man-made.

280
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:27,870
The mastermind is Consort Lan.

281
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:31,630
That vile woman!

282
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,030
She's so vicious.

283
00:14:33,790 --> 00:14:35,200
I will strip her of her title!

284
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,600
And revoke her position
as Noble Consort!

285
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,790
Sixi, deliver my order!

286
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:38,630
Your Majesty.

287
00:14:38,650 --> 00:14:40,150
The Empress Dowager
also knows about this.

288
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,600
She means don't
air family dirty laundry in public.

289
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:44,960
We must handle this quietly.

290
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:50,390
Calm down, Your Majesty.

291
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,910
It will harm your health.

292
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,910
Deliver the order.

293
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:59,320
Consort Lan is arrogant,

294
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,120
rude and defiant to imperial power.

295
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,440
Three months confined!

296
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:04,550
That Chief Eunuch Li

297
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:06,030
is extremely bold.

298
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:07,600
He plotted to harm the royal heir

299
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,720
and defied imperial orders.

300
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,030
Execute him immediately!

301
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,750
Yes, Your Majesty.

302
00:15:18,410 --> 00:15:20,850
♪I am but an outsider♪

303
00:15:20,890 --> 00:15:23,050
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

304
00:15:23,290 --> 00:15:27,330
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

305
00:15:27,330 --> 00:15:31,570
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

306
00:15:35,850 --> 00:15:39,090
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

307
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:42,650
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

308
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:45,170
♪I know how this story ends♪

309
00:15:45,170 --> 00:15:49,730
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

310
00:15:50,050 --> 00:15:54,170
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

311
00:15:59,130 --> 00:16:02,450
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

312
00:16:02,450 --> 00:16:05,730
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

313
00:16:05,930 --> 00:16:09,010
♪A history that no one can search♪

314
00:16:09,250 --> 00:16:12,530
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

315
00:16:12,570 --> 00:16:14,330
♪I am but an outsider♪

316
00:16:14,330 --> 00:16:16,570
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

317
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:20,610
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

318
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:25,290
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

319
00:16:29,210 --> 00:16:32,610
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

320
00:16:32,610 --> 00:16:35,970
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

321
00:16:35,970 --> 00:16:38,450
♪I know how this story ends♪

322
00:16:38,450 --> 00:16:42,610
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

323
00:16:42,610 --> 00:16:45,890
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

324
00:16:45,890 --> 00:16:49,690
♪Please forget me and move on♪

325
00:16:49,690 --> 00:16:55,930
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

326
00:16:59,090 --> 00:17:07,450
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

327
00:17:11,010 --> 00:17:20,730
♪When do I finally wake♪
